               <msContents>
                  <summary/>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i0">
                     <locus from="1v" to="14r">1v-14r</locus>
                     <textLang xml:lang="ar">Arabic</textLang>
                     <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT0049IHA#s16IHA">قران, Ninth ǧuz’ (9/30)</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="ar">
                        <locus target="#1v">-1v</locus>قَالَ المَلَلأُ الَّذِينَ اسْتَكْبَرُوْا مِنْ قَوْمِهِ لَـ[ـنخـ]ـرِ جَنَّكَ يَا شُعَيْبُ</incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="ar">
                        <locus target="#14r">-14r</locus>فَأَعْلَموْا اَنَّ اللهَ مَوْلَاكُمْ نِعْمَ المَوْلَيْ ونِعْمَ النَّصِيرُ</explicit>
                     <note>7:88-8:40.  Red verse markers formed as dots, commas or letters hā. Ihmāl marks (rā’-s). Some extensions of letters and words into the margin or words completed on the following line. Few words left uncompleted at the end of a line, and written in full on the following line. Vowels as well as some diacritics in lighter black ink, probably by another hand, sometimes with errors corrected. Numerous corrections. Catchwords. </note>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
